For optical simulation, the wavelength-dependent complex refractive index of the effective medium is calculated by a volume-weighted superposition of the QDs, WL, and GaAs material as described in [26], which is expressed by Eq. (1).1αeff=FQDαQD+FWLαWL+FGaAsαGaAs\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
